            <lg xml:id="TK742">
<l>maṇinīru maṇṇu malaiyu maṇiniḻaṟ</l>
<l>kāṭu muṭaiya taraṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fort is that which has everlasting water, plains, mountains and cool shady forests.</l>
